1.title: All Bottled Up
1.plot: Ryan Serhant attempts to impart his professional wisdom on Tim, a struggling wine salesman. The twist is he only has just one week to figure out what's holding Tim back and uncork his potential.

2.title: Wax On, Wax Off
2.plot: Ryan puts himself in some very sticky situations from getting waxed to convincing customers to get Brazilians and Manzilians.... He will do whatever it takes to prevent Mariel's boss from ripping her job away.

3.title: Coming Unhinged
3.plot: Ryan faces his hardest challenge yet: helping a salesperson who hasn't made a single sale... ever! Frank used to work in the restaurant business, but when his world got completely upended, his friend Paul got him a job selling kitchens and custom cabinets. The problem is, Frank doesn't know anything about kitchens, cabinets, or even selling! Ryan has to start at the root of the problem, not only professionally, but personally. If he can't figure out a blueprint for success, Frank's boss will close the door on him for good.

4.title: In Big Tub-ble
4.plot: Ryan has just one week to show a hot tub saleswoman how to save her business and have more fun in the process.

5.title: A Broker's Drive
5.plot: Erick was once his company's top apartment rental agent, but there's a new rival at his company, complete with a man-bun who is determined to take over Erick's spot and his clients. Sounds like a job for Ryan to tackle!

6.title: What Seams to be the Problem?
6.plot: Can Ryan help boost a struggling dress saleswoman's performance quickly, or will her hopes of keeping her job completely unravel?

7.title: A Broker's Breaking Point
7.plot: Ryan has one week to help who's Lisa the only woman at a boys-club commercial Real Estate brokerage. A situation made worse considering she has zero listings.

8.title: Pore Sales
8.plot: Ryan knows that when it comes to business, financials always come before family. This means he has to do everything he can to turn struggling sales associate Jen the caterpillar into Jenny the butterfly.

imdb.plot outline: Having cracked the world's most competitive real estate market, Ryan Serhant is hitting the road to put his skills to the test by providing his expertise to fellow agents in need. In the process of learning the tricks of a particular trade, he'll also help an under-performing salesperson become a selling shark just like him.
imdb.title: Sell it Like Serhant
plot: Having cracked the world's most competitive real estate market, Ryan Serhant is hitting the road to put his skills to the test by providing his expertise to fellow agents in need. In the process of learning the tricks of a particular trade, he'll also help an under-performing salesperson become a selling shark just like him.

Ryan Serhant knows a thing or two about how to make a sale. The star of "Million Dollar Listing New York" has demonstrated his sales skills time and time again as the leader of one of the top real estate teams in New York. Now, Ryan is eager to lend his expertise to struggling sales representatives across a wide range of industries in "_Sell it Like Serhant_ (qv)." The series follows Ryan as he immerses himself in different trades outside of real estate and attempts to teach lackluster salespeople how to close the deal.
